    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "――え？　僕にまた演技の仕事？\nこの間もやらなかったっけ？",
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、前回の仕事が好評で\nぜひ葵にとオファーが来ているんだ",
      "startTime": 10.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。ふーん",
      "startTime": 12.911904494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり乗り気ではなさそうだな",
      "startTime": 15.5595914681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、僕はLizNoirのメンバーだから\n本業はあくまで歌とダンスだよ",
      "startTime": 21.8106074174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "役者になりたい訳じゃないし",
      "startTime": 24.7226526101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言うと思ったけど、一応原作を読んでみないか？\n先方から預かってきたんだ",
      "startTime": 31.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4399.999999999998,
          "startTime": 35.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6690.000000000005,
          "startTime": 38.09
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、原作は漫画なんだ。僕でも知ってる作品だね\n好きだよ、これ",
      "startTime": 40.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　知らないと思ってた\n少し前の作品だし、男性向けの漫画だから",
      "startTime": 45.2999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "兄貴が持ってたからね\n僕も、暇な時に読んでたんだ",
      "startTime": 51.1333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "確か、主人公が女の子じゃなかったかな？\n悪の組織に復讐する、アクションものだったはずだよ",
      "startTime": 57.5666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}